OL,3,CWeeks until bridge 'love locks' are
OL,4,Csold for scrap, council warns
OL,6,FPeople who have attached so-called
OL,7,F"love locks" to a Derbyshire bridge
OL,8,Fhave been given less than two months
OL,9,Fto remove them before they are
OL,10,Fscrapped.
OL,12,FAn estimated 5,000 padlocks have been
OL,13,Ffixed to the Weir footbridge in
OL,14,FBakewell by people celebrating
OL,15,Frelationships or remembering loved
OL,16,Fones since 2011.
OL,18,FBut a major repair project will start
OL,19,Fin September to deal with rust and
OL,20,Frepair the bridge's walkways.
