OL,3,CWeeks until bridge 'love locks' are
OL,4,Csold for scrap, council warns
OL,6,FCllr Charlotte Cupit, Derbyshire
OL,7,FCounty Council's cabinet member for
OL,8,Fhighways, said: "We can only do these
OL,9,Fworks by removing all the padlocks
OL,10,Fattached to the bridge.
OL,12,F"Whilst we know that views are divided
OL,13,Fover the overall presence of the locks
OL,14,Fon the bridge, we understand the
OL,15,Fimportance of individual locks that
OL,16,Fhave been placed on the bridge to
OL,17,Fmany, so we are working hard to carry
OL,18,Fout these essential repairs in the
OL,19,Fmost sensitive and responsible way we
OL,20,Fcan.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
