OL,3,CWeeks until bridge 'love locks' are
OL,4,Csold for scrap, council warns
OL,6,F"In recognition of the significance of
OL,7,Fthe footbridge to many people, we are
OL,8,Foffering people the opportunity to
OL,9,Fcome forward now to remove their 'love
OL,10,Flock' before the work is due to start."
OL,12,FUnder the repair scheme, the bridge,
OL,13,Fwhich was installed in 1997, will be
OL,14,Ftreated for rust damage, repainted and
OL,15,Fgiven new railings and a reinforced
OL,16,Fglass fibre walkway.
OL,18,FThe work was due to take place in
OL,19,F2021, but was delayed to consider
OL,20,Fpossible options for the locks.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
