OL,3,CWeeks until bridge 'love locks' are
OL,4,Csold for scrap, council warns
OL,6,FSuch is the strength of feeling that a
OL,7,Fdedicated Facebook group was set up to
OL,8,Ftry to find an alternative location
OL,9,Ffor the locks. The Save the Love Locks
OL,10,Fat Bakewell page has more than 1,000
OL,11,Fmembers.
OL,13,FThe council said any locks that are
OL,14,Fnot removed before 16 September will
OL,15,Fbe removed and recycled, with the
OL,16,Fproceeds going to two local charities.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
