OL,6,FCllr Cupit added: "We've planned the
OL,7,Ftiming of these repairs for after the
OL,8,Fschool holidays to both minimise
OL,9,Fdisruption but also to give the summer
OL,10,Fperiod for people to remove their lock
OL,11,Ffrom the bridge if they would like to."
